OL,3,CEmergency services respond to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cincident' in Lake District
OL,6,FEmergency services are attending an
OL,7,F'ongoing incident' in the Lake
OL,8,FDistrict.
OL,10,FFirefighters are currently at the
OL,11,Fscene at High Dam Tarn, near
OL,12,FWindermere, according to a post from
OL,13,Fthe Cumbria Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Freleased at 2pm on Tuesday April 7.
OL,16,FEmergency services have cordoned off
OL,17,Fthe area, with a police officer
OL,18,Fblocking the path to the scene.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
