OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775581553
OL,3,CEmergency services respond to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cincident' in Lake District
OL,6,FThe fire service has asked people to
OL,7,Favoid the area while it responds to
OL,8,Fthe incident.
OL,10,FPolice officers, mountain rescue
OL,11,Fvolunteers, rescue helicopters, and an
OL,12,Fair ambulance are also at the scene,
OL,13,Faccording to the 'North Yorkshire
OL,14,FWeather Updates' Facebook page.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
