OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775581553
OL,3,CEmergency services respond to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cincident' in Lake District
OL,6,FOne woman, Lisa Morris, commented on
OL,7,Fthis post, saying: "I think we've
OL,8,Fcounted three fire engines, two fire
OL,9,Fcars, four police, two ambulances, two
OL,10,Fambulance cars, air ambulance, search
OL,11,Fand rescue helicopter and two Mountain
OL,12,FRescue vehicles."
OL,14,FCumbria Police has told ITV Border
OL,15,Fthat the force cannot reveal any
OL,16,Fdetails yet, but will release a
OL,17,Fstatement in due course.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
